nodes.text: Vinzen Neela 5 was a planet located within the Vinzen Neela system of the Outer Rim Territories.

It was the site of a major Rebel defeat. After the Battle of Hoth, they tried to thwart an Imperial transfer of prototype TIE Defenders to the Ton-Falk-class escort carrier Hininbirg. The attack was repelled by Imperial pilot Maarek Stele.
